			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi guys, Progression here  (65 Bard)-- I was hoping that someone could help me out with tip on Swarming the Garg's in PoN. There isn't too much detailed info on this...
<br />

<br />
I tried doing it once, I triggered a trap and had to zone it... 
<br />

<br />
How do you pull them out without triggering anything? ...and I hear there are some summoning mobs?     
<br />
Also what about casters??
<br />

<br />
Any info would help me, I'd really appreciate this... Watching a Bard swarming gargs is what inspired me to make a bard my new main <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />

<br />
I dont need any swarming tips or anything, just on this specific camp....Thanks so much for your time!!!
<br />

<br />
Progression --- 65 Maestro of Quellious</span></td>
