				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarming Gargs! Veterans please give me some advice!<a name="23375"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 24 04 1:18 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I swarm gargs on occasion, but I never venture into the city. I only pull the gargs that spawn on top of the wall. I can get 10 or so this way and don't have to go inside to get them. There are lots of banshees inside that summon. You could always highsun them back, but this will only work if you plan on pulling the gargs away from the city. I prefer to stay right outside the wall which doesnt get me far enough away from their spawn point.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
